                    <span>As a typical instruction-manual-phobic kinda guy, this is a delight. The real clincher is the well-presented DVD tutorial, so I can sit back and learn on "autopilot". <P>...<P>This is the sort of guide that Apple should be shipping with every Mac.<P>...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">At last... a how-to book that delivers value for money</div>
